CTD on Game Launch

    Ensure SKSE64 is correctly installed.

    Verify Engine Fixes is active and configured.

    Check that all mods have their dependencies installed.

Black or Discolored Faces

    Face Discoloration Fix SE is included; ensure it's active.

    If it persists, regenerate Facegen in the Creation Kit.

Physics Not Working

    Verify CBPC and Faster HDT-SMP are active.

    Ensure XPMSSE is installed and loaded correctly.

Lux or Lighting Issues

    Check that all Lux patches are active and in the correct order.

    Run Lux - Patch Hub to regenerate patches if you add new mods.

DynDOLOD / xLODGen

    If you see terrain patches or incorrect LODs, regenerate the outputs.

    Ensure you have enough memory and disk space.
